status_desc: A user story is created with a title only and other  information (system assigned)
A user story is available to being worked on (edited and reviewed) by one or more authors (system assigned or Human Input)
A user story is actively being worked on (edited and reviewed) by one or more authors (system assigned or Human Input)
A user story whose score is >= US_QTS
A user story assigned to an Iteration
A user story completed in an Iteration
A user story archived for historical purposes.
